An [[Optimization]] problem that can be specified by a linear (I hope you remember [[Linear Algebra]]...) [[Objective]] function and linear inequality constraints; in other words, problems of the form:

* minimize $$\vec c^T \vec x$$
* subject to $$A\vec x \preceq \vec b$$

With $$\vec x, \vec c \in \R^n$$, $$A \in \R^{m\times n}$$, $$\vec b \in \R^m$$.